OL,3,CCracking news Gromit! New Royal Mint
OL,4,C50p coin celebrates 50 years of Aardman
OL,6,FCollectable coins celebrating 50 years
OL,7,Fof Aardman, the Academy Award-winning
OL,8,Fanimation studio behind beloved
OL,9,Fcharacters such as Wallace and Gromit
OL,10,Fand Shaun the Sheep, are being
OL,11,Flaunched by The Royal Mint.
OL,13,FThe "tails" side of the coin was
OL,14,Fdesigned by Aardman and features some
OL,15,Fof the most recognisable characters
OL,16,Ffrom the studio's back catalogue.
OL,18,FThe design includes Morph, Shaun the
OL,19,FSheep and scheming villain Feathers
OL,20,FMcGraw, as well as Wallace and Gromit.
OL,26,@uD@EOUuD@KO]
