OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1781010670
OL,3,CCracking news Gromit! New Royal Mint
OL,4,C50p coin celebrates 50 years of Aardman
OL,6,FA selection of the coins will also
OL,7,Fbring the designs to life in colour.
OL,9,FTo mark the launch, Aardman co-founder
OL,10,FPeter Lord visited The Royal Mint to
OL,11,Fstrike one of the first of the 50p
OL,12,Fcoins.
OL,14,FAardman, known for its stop-motion
OL,15,Fstyle of filming, whereby characters
OL,16,Fare moved in small increments, is an
OL,17,Femployee-owned company based in
OL,18,FBristol.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
