OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1781010670
OL,3,CCracking news Gromit! New Royal Mint
OL,4,C50p coin celebrates 50 years of Aardman
OL,6,FIt has been entertaining viewers since
OL,7,Fthe 1970s, building generations of
OL,8,Ffans.
OL,10,FMorph featured on the children's art
OL,11,Fprogramme Take Hart.
OL,13,FThe farmyard antics of Shaun the Sheep
OL,14,Fand Timmy have also charmed viewers,
OL,15,Fas have cheese-loving inventor Wallace
OL,16,Fand his loyal dog Gromit who often
OL,17,Fgets him out of trouble.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
