SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1781010670
OL,3,CCracking news Gromit! New Royal Mint
OL,4,C50p coin celebrates 50 years of Aardman
OL,6,FThis year sees the studio celebrate
OL,7,Fits 50th anniversary with events and
OL,8,Fcelebrations highlighting the craft
OL,9,Fand legacy of Aardman and with the
OL,10,Flaunch of a new film, Shaun The Sheep:
OL,11,FThe Beast Of Mossy Bottom, in the
OL,12,Fautumn.
OL,14,FRebecca Morgan, director at The Royal
OL,15,FMint, said: "Aardman characters have
OL,16,Fbeen part of the fabric of British
OL,17,Flife for 50 years, and the nostalgia
OL,18,Fthey carry is truly extraordinary.
OL,26,@wD@MOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
