OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1781010670
OL,3,CCracking news Gromit! New Royal Mint
OL,4,C50p coin celebrates 50 years of Aardman
OL,6,F"Whether you grew up watching Wallace
OL,7,Fand Gromit on Christmas Day, fell in
OL,8,Flove with Morph as a child, or
OL,9,Fintroduced Shaun the Sheep to a new
OL,10,Fgeneration, these characters hold a
OL,11,Fvery special place in people's hearts."
OL,13,FMr Lord said: "I'm very proud that the
OL,14,Fstory of Aardman, and the characters
OL,15,Fwe've created over the last 50 years,
OL,16,Fare being celebrated by the work of
OL,17,FThe Royal Mint.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@gO]uD@OOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
