OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1781010670
OL,3,CCracking news Gromit! New Royal Mint
OL,4,C50p coin celebrates 50 years of Aardman
OL,6,F"It was such a pleasure to visit and
OL,7,Fsee for myself, close up, the amazing
OL,8,Fcare and artistry that goes into
OL,9,Fmaking these beautiful coins.
OL,11,F"In fact, the whole place reminded me
OL,12,Fof the Aardman studio ` both are full
OL,13,Fof super-talented artists and
OL,14,Fcraftspeople creating timeless work.
OL,16,F"We love to bring pleasure and fun to
OL,17,Four audiences, and these fabulous
OL,18,Fcoins surely represent that joyous
OL,19,Fspirit."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUxD@AOU{D@HO]
