OL,3,CCracking news Gromit! New Royal Mint
OL,4,C50p coin celebrates 50 years of Aardman
OL,6,FA gold version of the Aardman 50p will
OL,7,Fbe produced from recycled gold, coming
OL,8,Ffrom old jewellery and coins.
OL,10,FThe Royal Mint said it aims to extend
OL,11,Fthis approach to all of its
OL,12,Fcollectable gold coins by the end of
OL,13,F2026.
OL,15,FThe coins will be available to buy
OL,16,Ffrom 9am on Tuesday June 9 from The
OL,17,FRoyal Mint's website.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
